*************************************************************
***** SOME C CODES TO BE USED AS EXAMPLES WHEN TEACHING *****
***********  MCMC, PATH-INTEGRAL, QUANTUM FIELDS  ***********
*************************************************************

bad_rng : an example of a terrible random number generator 
          (look at the result in 3d...)

pi_no_rng: non stochastic determination of pi

pi_rng: pi determined by simple sampling

gauss_rng: test of the Box-Muller polar method to generate
           random number with Gaussian distribution
